 <section id="glass-materials">
   <div class="wrap">
     <div class="sec-num">03½ — Material Science</div>
     <h2 class="sec-title">Glass Material Library</h2>
     <p class="sec-sub">Glass is a <em>material</em>, not a theme effect. Structural properties — opacity, blur, saturation — are constant across dark/light. Only the tint inverts.</p>
     <div class="glass-grid">
       <div class="gcard frosted">FROSTED</div>
